    "description": "Daitron Co., Ltd., an electronic engineering trading company, engages in electronic equipment and components, and manufacturing equipment businesses in Japan and internationally. The company manufactures, sells, imports, and exports electronic components and assembly goods, semiconductors, embedded systems, power supply equipment, image-related equipment and components, information systems, FPD manufacturing equipment, electronic components manufacturing equipment, etc. It provides connector harnesses; optical and image processing devices; factory automation PCs for equipment control and other IT equipment; RFID, IC, and biometric identification devices; teleconferencing video system; and other electronic components. In addition, the company provides manufacturing equipment for electronic materials and devices; OPT devices; flat panel display; high-performance film; secondary battery; transportation and automation; and environment and accessory. The company was formerly known as Daito Electron Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Daitron Co., Ltd. in 2017. Daitron Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1952 and is based in Osaka, Japan."
